<table>
<colgroup>
<col style="width: 100%" />
</colgroup>
<tbody>
<tr class="odd">
<td><p>Minimum: 0</p>
<p>Maximum: 1</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>

## Remarks

This is the value in weeks for the default length for new sprints. For example, if the value is 2 that is treated as 2 weeks.

